# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_HAS_LANDING_GEAR

## Summary
Returns whether a vehicle has a landing gear (all planes and some helicopters)

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **BOOL**
